headline: UGG Unveils ‘Iconic From the First Step’ Campaign for Autumn/Winter 2025
summary: SANTA BARBARA, Calif., August 21, 2025--Southern California-based global lifestyle brand UGG® (a division of Deckers Brands [NYSE: DECK]) releases its Autumn/Winter 2025 campaign, Iconic From the First Step.
